## PRD Clarification (When Needed)

If the PRD has ambiguities, present **lettered options** for quick resolution.

### Format Questions Like This

```markdown
Before I generate tasks, I need clarification on a few points:

1. What is the primary deployment target?
   A. Kubernetes (production cluster)
   B. Docker Compose (dev/staging)
   C. Both with different configs
   D. Other: [please specify]

2. What authentication approach?
   A. Better Auth (recommended for new projects)
   B. Auth0/Clerk (existing integration)
   C. Custom JWT implementation
   D. SSO/SAML enterprise

3. What database preference?
   A. PostgreSQL (CloudNative-PG operator)
   B. MySQL/MariaDB
   C. MongoDB (Percona operator)
   D. Use existing database

Please respond with format: "1A, 2A, 3A" for quick answers.
```

### When to Ask

| PRD Content | Clarification Needed? |
|-------------|----------------------|
| "Build a notification system" | Yes - scope unclear |
| "Add user authentication" | Yes - which provider? |
| "Integrate with Slack" | No - specific enough |
| "Make it scalable" | Yes - what scale? |
| "Use our standard stack" | Maybe - if not defined |

### Keep Clarifications Minimal

- Only ask 3-5 essential questions
- Focus on architecture-impacting decisions
- Skip questions the PRD already answers
- Default to best practices when reasonable

